{"type": "article", "id": 33369, "title": "上海时装周持续更新，以及，隈研吾设计的银制茶具看看就好 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-10-17T02:47:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 33826, "name": "2016 上海时装周"}, {"id": 33987, "name": "茶道银器"}, {"id": 33991, "name": "卢布贬值"}, {"id": 33992, "name": "俄罗斯奢侈品市场"}, {"id": 977, "name": "Tom Ford"}, {"id": 3472, "name": "周大福"}, {"id": 5228, "name": "UGG"}, {"id": 24876, "name": "黑石集团"}, {"id": 33993, "name": "David Yurman"}, {"id": 893, "name": "隈研吾"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161017095928vbEYqNwBliz9TjSJ.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-10-13/blackrock-increases-stake-in-world-s-biggest-jewelry-retailer\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>黑石集团增持了周大福的股份</b></a> | 尽管周大福在今年表现不佳，截止至 6 月底的三个月内，由于大陆游客的减少，周大福香港和澳门的同店销售额同比下降了 20%。全球最大的资产管理公司，美国黑石集团（BlackRock）最近增持了周大福集团的股份。据 Bloomberg 数据显示，截止至 8 月 31 日，黑石持有 104 万股周大福的股票。不过，黑石对于增持周大福一事不予置评。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/david-yurman-expands-in-dubai-with-two-new-stores/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国珠宝品牌  David Yurman 进军迪拜市场</b></a> | David Yurman 是一个创立于 1979 年的美国珠宝品牌。它在迪拜新开了两家店，分别位于迪拜的 Bloomingdale’s 和 Harvey Nichols。至今，David Yurman 在北美和全球范围内共有超过 30 家门店。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/russias-luxury-market-benefits-from-devaluated-ruble/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>由于卢布贬值，奢侈品在俄罗斯当地市场变得更有吸引力</b></a> | 根据欧睿咨询的数据显示，由于卢布贬值，奢侈品的价格在俄罗斯当地市场更有吸引力。越来越多人选择在当地购物，俄罗斯同样也吸引着外国游客前来旅游消费。在俄罗斯，使用卢布购买奢侈品的人数增加了 2%，相比之下，使用美元购买购买奢侈品的则下降了 30%。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">上海时装周持续更新：</p><p class=\"\">GALATEA 葛澜是一个创立已十年的原创婚纱定制品牌。它的名字源于希腊爱情故事，风格上以英伦风为基调，融入了东方式的典雅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235512sl0XNZW9QyIeFVLS.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235516WRX8FG6fl5h0Iydt.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499303\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235517kto24islJd5QLRNh.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235517chg5ny01vex7ISC2.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500460\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235520qahuGbERQwyKWCos.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500466\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235525lqhUGjy4Pp8JeOVw.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235527TMuXVinW5yF6r8As.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235527do2hJ10CTxrzGQDF.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235528cnvK7O9f5xhSNuGL.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500223\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">YAKI HIDOMI 是来自日本的设计师同名品牌。设计师 Yaki Hidomi（八木瞳) 以一贯别出心裁的手法结合 1945s 军用面料，发布主题为 “Metamorphosis” 的 2017 春夏系列。</p><p>          </p><p>          </p><p>          </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235638rZlnJd4BSiMGLKsf.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499782\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235642EuPADT7Nd6YcZK05.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235643iHzSByUTELdt82Ch.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610162356432J0xZkG98KXFunvt.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500238\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235644ynfEABbT1Np6MSig.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101623564515EFCkLNYoliJzT0.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Jade en Plus（加是）是由设计师唐佳在 2007 年创立的女装品牌。2017 春夏系列以电影《小姐》作为灵感来源，从日本文化中汲取灵感，将日式复古融入在法式优雅之中。</p><p>          </p><p>          </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235749Sr3IYoXLstq5B6e0.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500473\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235752Md9uRZrQmolD8yKS.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235753ZCo71qDMlhe0dJHL.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500217\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235753gCOL1nYzDWxEo9S0.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500211\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235754glJrsdMkeVXLS9A4.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500473\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235801r3mltqDO2esyvzRF.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235800oHzi8mOvXKS6Z4Jr.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016235801C4voq1zaNujpSFnl.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610162358011S75toB3ZwIkbn8L.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500428\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/ugg-x-white-mountaineering\" rel=\"nofollow\">UGG 与  White Mountaineering 合作</a>，推出了一个兼具设计和实用性的新款雪地靴系列。该系列包括以全羊皮打造的男士靴款，以及另一个以 UGG 经典设计为基础的中性鞋款。这个系列将于 10 月 22 日在日本限定发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017095404INq4ilvtZsHSh8ez.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017095415hyEV0Nf1F4pWqdnx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017095424xbVOSlMRqZGrk4f6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">丹麦银器名店 Georg Jensen 与隈研吾合作，推出了首套名为<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/georg-jensen-kengo-kuma-sliver-tea-set\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Kusa</a> 的茶道银器组合。这款银制茶具结合了西方的银器制作工艺和东方的茶艺。这也是擅长木作的隈研吾首次使用纯银作为设计材料，作品中也透露出了日式东方禅意。不过，这套银制茶具全球限定发售 11 套，看看就好。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017095259qohFP1Ewzx5H0DA9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610170953140OGgZ2yu8K6YfnUo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017095324bXlQ5uDhyN6BjRan.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610170953349FZuPlyhqx5nsAUj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017095343Lw0AyifBHkW56XM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017095351bv8hPYHRxicQVS96.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Tom Ford 推出全新的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/tom-ford-private-blend-vert-des-bois\" rel=\"nofollow\">  Les Extraits Verts</a> 系列香水。这系列香水以青涩的木芽香为主调，共有 4 个不同的版本，Vert de Fleur 与 Vert Bohéme 属花系，Vert des Bois 与 Vert d’Encens 属木系。Vert des Bois 亲和而活泼，气味宜人持久。 Vert d’Encens 则混合了薰衣草、柠檬和辛香，气味较复杂。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017095231UWsItZSx0dvmT61G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101709524273SHkNYdbmvy0Lfe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017095250fEtLvx716Alkn02J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}